</p>

</div>
<div id="fn" class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#GEWN-02-10-02-0247-fn-0001-ptr" id="GEWN-02-10-02-0247-fn-0001">1</a>

   <p>The last allotment of land under the terms of Dinwiddies Proclamation of 1754 was made in November 1773. See <a href="default.xqy?keys=GEWN-print-02-09-02-0283" class="document">GW to Dunmore and Council, c.3 Nov. 1773, and notes</a>.</p>

</div>
<div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#GEWN-02-10-02-0247-fn-0002-ptr" id="GEWN-02-10-02-0247-fn-0002">2</a>

   <p>This order in council was dated 15 Dec. 1769 (<span class="ref-st" title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ H. R. McIlwaine et al., eds. &lt;i&gt;Executive Journals of the Council of Colonial Virginia&lt;/i&gt;. 6 vols. Richmond, 192566. ]"><span class="hi-italic" style="font-style: italic;">Exec. Journals of Virginia Council</span></span>, 6:338).</p>

</div>
<div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#GEWN-02-10-02-0247-fn-0003-ptr" id="GEWN-02-10-02-0247-fn-0003">3</a>

   <p>See <a href="default.xqy?keys=GEWN-print-02-09-02-0085" class="document">Petition to Dunmore and Virginia Council, c.4 Nov. 1772</a>.</p>

</div>
<div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#GEWN-02-10-02-0247-fn-0004-ptr" id="GEWN-02-10-02-0247-fn-0004">4</a>

   <p>See <a href="default.xqy?keys=GEWN-print-02-10-02-0262" class="document">Dunmore to GW, 18 April</a>.</p>

